# Telegram Bot credentials
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your real values.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Step 1: Create a bot
#   Open Telegram → search for @BotFather → send /newbot
#   Follow the prompts, then copy the token it gives you:
TELEGRAM_TOKEN=8252468955:dslkvbsbk


# Step 2: Find your chat ID
#   Start a conversation with your new bot (send it any message).
#   Then open this URL in a browser (replace <TOKEN> with your token):
#     https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates
#   Look for:  "chat": { "id": <THIS_NUMBER> }
#   Paste that number here:
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=34482464537593
